###STEPS TO BE FOLLOWED TO CREATE THE PERSONAL PROTFOLIO USINGNG MERN STACK ###

1. started with the backend and the filename is backend_protfolio
2. installed 
|===> npm init 
3. next install all the availabe packages required
|===> npm install express express-fileupload bcrypt cookie-parser nodemailer cors dotenv cloudinary jsonwebtoken mongoose
4. create 
|==> app.js file
5. Go to package.json file and add
|===> "type":"module"  and 
|===> in scripts add "start":"node server.js" , "dev":"nodemon server.js"
6. create
|==> server.js file
7. install nodemon if not there
|===> npm install -g nodemon
8. npm run dev --> to run the backend code [developing stage]


